---
title: Crispy Buffalo Chicken Sandwiches with Potato Wedges & Blue Cheese Dressing
description: Happy buffalo chicken night! You’ll brush crispy panko fried chicken with tangy, buttery, spicy buffalo sauce (you know the one!), then tuck into a toasted brioche bun spread with blue cheese sauce and layered with marinated cucumber for fresh, crunchy contrast. On the side are crispy potato wedges with more blue cheese dressing for dipping.
